name: Travel For Teens
tag_list: student-travel, student-trips, travel, tours, trips, traveling, education
overview: We work with you to design your idea of the perfect trip at prices comparable to the uninspired, boiler plate sightseeing tours offered elsewhere. This does not translate into expensive customization. We fashion wonderful trips that work with a wide variety of budgets and preferences. Schools, families, clubs, associations… groups of any type can have the trip of a lifetime with all the choices anyone could want.
